{"tid":1589361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田大會堂五星旗被拆 擺商場任人踩 再揼落城門河","createTime":"2019-09-23T09:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:31:05.000Z","uid":135077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc1524f79bead523fe9bb5a580354aa0b777692","tid":1589361,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"今日（22日）在沙田新城市廣場內，有市民聚集，向支持政府的商戶抗議。其間有市民到沙田大會堂外旗桿，將中華人民共和國國旗降下，並將其帶到新城市廣場中庭內，讓在場市民踐踏及塗污。不久後有市民將被塗污的國旗，放進垃圾桶內並拋進商場外的水池。在場市民大叫「何君堯，大個仔啦，識游水啦」及「護旗手係邊啊？何君堯浸親啦！」後來有市民把國旗拾回，並扔進城門河中。<br />\n<br />\n除塗污國旗外，有市民焚燒在沙田新城市廣場外的京奧標誌，並在標誌下貼上「赤納粹」貼紙。其後被一名白衣男子弄熄，示威者隨即擁上並爭相與其合照，及在他背上貼「赤納粹」貼紙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190922&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60072315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190922%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60072315&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4d426b16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190922%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60072315&h=ec551ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190922&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60072315</a><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沙田損毀國旗 1男子被捕</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方指，昨日有示威者在沙田新城市廣場損毀國旗，更將國旗投入沙田城門河。有組織罪案及三合會調查科人員經深入調查後，昨晚拘捕一名21歲姓羅本地男子，涉嫌「侮辱國旗」。被捕男子現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n昨午大批市民聚集沙田新城市廣場，有示威者破壞商場內的設施，並拆下沙田大會堂的國旗，放在地上踐踏，再拋落城門河。警方其後清場，示威者撤離時多次設路障和燒雜物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190923&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60073760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190923%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60073760&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=3c53d0d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190923%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60073760&h=b19de656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190923&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60073760</a>"},{"pid":"497952959a5f6a309f969c38cdd00a108da9dbea","tid":1589361,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2214e6f198c807f01f44060e44a1c4f7734dc5d","tid":1589361,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"點拉到果位手足？"},{"pid":"12176986b17693697f9957861313d31305f28ba3","tid":1589361,"uid":293937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2214e6f198c807f01f44060e44a1c4f7734dc5d","tid":1589361,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"點拉到果位手足？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"bbcf7921da2a98c19d284318e9627af56fc625e9","tid":1589361,"uid":135077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd290e7bd35bef5ff61fd12616e7618b65533bb","tid":1589361,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"咁大個啡袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77767e7dcbb15b3d355d6d15c3e2e923390e8e82","tid":1589361,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}